-- Asset manager Legg Mason to buy UK's Martin Currie 
-- 
-- Thu Jul 24, 2014 08:38AM EDT
-- None



July 24 (Reuters) - Asset manager Legg Mason Inc <LM.N> said it would buy UK-based investment manager Martin Currie to expand in equity markets.

The deal is expected to be slightly accretive to Legg Mason's earnings in the first year and is expected to close during the fourth quarter of 2014, the purchaser said in a statement.[ID:nPn9Qwdlx]